  "synopsis": "Yu-yu, Raika, and Touya were invited to America after their win in the “Deluxe” tournament in Japan, and went on a tour of exhibition matches.\n\nIt was one blazing fight after another as their opponents were all top ranking fighters from Deluxe USA. Danji, who had arrived earlier in America to look into the background of the Deluxe tournament at Michiru’s behest, begins to suspect a connection with the case of the missing fighters.\n\nMeanwhile, a new force emerges in Japan, with their ideal of achieving the “Ultimate Fight” in cardfights.\n\nWhat is their goal of recruiting more and more fighters? This will eventually come to cast a shadow upon the future of Yu-yu and the rest of Blackout…\n\n(Source: cf-vanguard.com)",
